&lt;li&gt;Strong verbal and written communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with complex excel files, PowerBI and PowerPoint presentations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow up skills and acute attention to accuracy and detail are essential&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in English is a must (verbal and written)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
